Class LogCatHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sirqul.sdk.helpers.LogCatHelper

  • public class LogCatHelper
extends Object
    The Class LogCatHelper. Essentially everything that the native LogCat functions perform, but will issue additional entries for messages over 4,000 characters in length.
    Author:
    John Schleppy
